MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

96-1761. State ex rel. Diesman v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 95APD09-1175. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of the application for dismissal of appellants, Industrial Commission of Ohio and Administrator, Ohio Bureau of Workers’ Compensation,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective November 14,1996.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
